<h1>Eldest director</h1>

<% if @eldest_director.dob.nil?%>
  <p>The eldest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%=@eldest_director.id%>"><%=@eldest_director.name%></a>.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>The eldest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%=@eldest_director.id%>"><%=@eldest_director.name%></a>, born on<%=@eldest_director.dob.strftime(" %B %d, %Y")%>.</p>
  <p>

  <% end %>
  (<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)
</p>
